
Docker Run Commands for Teekay - VBS,IA,RM
===========================================

sudo docker run --name teekay-mysql -p 3307:3306 --restart unless-stopped -e MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD=R@@Tt@@kY -v /home/centos/DATA/MySQL-Container-Data/conf.d:/etc/mysql/conf.d -v /home/centos/DATA/MySQL-Container-Data/mysql:/var/lib/mysql -d mysql/mysql-server:5.7.20


VBS
===

sudo docker run -d --net=host --restart unless-stopped -v /home/centos/DATA/mount-point/vbs_rulesheet:/home/shareuser/newshare teekay_service_v2
sudo docker run -d --net=host --restart unless-stopped -v /home/centos/DATA/mount-point/vbs_rulesheet:/home/shareuser/newshare teekay_datajob_v2
sudo docker run -d --net=host --restart unless-stopped teekay_html_v3


Injury
======

sudo docker run -d --net=host --restart unless-stopped -v /home/centos/DATA/mount-point/Injury_Analysis:/home/Injury_analysis injury_java
sudo docker run -d --net=host --restart unless-stopped injury_frontend_2

RiskMapping
===========
sudo docker run -d --net=host --restart unless-stopped -v /home/centos/DATA/mount-point/Risk_Teekay:/home/teekay rm_java_4
sudo docker run -d --net=host --restart unless-stopped -v /home/centos/DATA/mount-point/Risk_Teekay:/home/teekay rm_python
sudo docker run -d --net=host --restart unless-stopped rm_frontend_3




Mount Points:
=============

SYNTAX:  <PHYSICAL_MOUNT>:<CONTAINER_MOUNT>

/home/centos/DATA/mount-point/vbs_rulesheet:/home/shareuser/newshare

/home/centos/DATA/mount-point/Injury_Analysis:/home/Injury_analysis

/home/centos/DATA/mount-point/Risk_Teekay:/home/teekay


